Scan today's cartoon by Bethuel Mangena to experience an AR video of how he got the cartoon done. Stories and adverts in #SatStar as well as Independent Media titles across South Africa, are now augmented. Editorial and advertising augmented reality (AR+) experience allows you, the reader, to access exciting content using your smartphone or tablet while reading the newspaper.To access AR content follow these steps: 1. First, you need to download the IOL app in your app store - it's available for both iOS and Android.2. Whenever you see an AR logo on a picture or article in the paper, open your IOL app3. Tap the camera button4. Tap "SCAN" and aim your camera at the picture. The following is a video of Mangena going through his entire process of drawing a cartoon.  To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
    supports HTML5 video This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window. AR content also includes slideshows, one click purchases and other digital links to help you get the best out of your reading experience. The Saturday Star